title: The Phantom Stranger 00-18 (2012- |Digital|TheGroup+Empire+)
description:
Dan Didio writes this New 52 series which updates the Phantom Stranger for the modern DC Universe. Brent Anderson and others share writing duties. Promotional info from the first collected edition - "Who has been sacrificed? Who is guilty? Who can save us? And who...is The Phantom Stranger? Cursed for a betrayal that affected the very course of history, the Stranger walks the Earth attempting to atone for his sins. His actions have consequences, and as he fulfils his duty, the people he encounters will never be the same. This series re-introduces a number of DC Comics characters into the New 52, including the Spectre, Raven, and Dr. 13."

This all the first 19 issues of the series in digital format. After issue 08, the series was renamed under the "Trinity of Sin" banner imprint. The scanners are TheGroup, Cypher and Son of Ultron-Empire, all of varying resolutions (the credits are listed in each title). Thanks to them for their efforts, please seed and enjoy! :-)
